<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((صحيح أبي داود)</span>) <span class="c2">(١٨٣٨)</span> <span class="c2">((الإرواء)</span>) <span class="c2">(٦/ ٣٤٥/١٢٤٥)</span>: ق.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>